or Wilson's furry friends. This facility features spacious exercise zones, North Carolina pet care professionals, offering pet...\",\"address\":{\"@type\":\"PostalAddress\",\"addressLocality\":\"Wilson\",\"addressRegion\":\"NC\",\"addressCountry\":\"US\"},\"image\":\"/images/parks/northcarolina/points-east-veterinary-specialty-hospital/points-east-veterinary-specialty-hospital-1.jpg\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Where is the Wilson Dog Park?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"The Wilson Dog Park is located at 1413 Lawndale Dr. It’s a fenced facility with separate areas for large and small dogs, plus agility tunnels.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are dogs allowed at the Whirligig Park?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes! Leashed dogs are welcome in Vollis Simpson Whirligig Park. It’s a unique spot for a walk, but keep an eye on your dog around the moving sculptures.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Does Wilson have greenways?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, the Wilson Greenway System is growing. The beautifully paved path around Lake Wilson is a particularly scenic spot for a 2-mile dog walk.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the leash laws in Wilson?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Dogs must be on a leash and under physical control when off the owner’s property. Wilson takes animal control seriously to ensure public safety.\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Dog Parks Directory\",\"item\":\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\