span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">12</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">FAQs</span></button></li><li class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-item  \"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-link\"><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-number\">13</span><span class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-text\">More Resources</span></button></li></ul></nav><div class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-actions\"><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn toc-action-top\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-up\"></i>Back to Top</button><button class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 toc-action-btn\"><i class=\"jsx-75d84499fe54ac73 bi bi-arrow-down\"></i>To Bottom</button></div></div></div><main class=\"city-page-layout\"><div class=\"mobile-toc-button\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"mobile-toc-trigger\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-ul\"></i><span>Contents</span></button></div><section id=\"city-hero\" class=\"city-hero-section \"><div class=\"section-shell city-hero-shell\"><div class=\"city-hero-copy\"><div class=\"hero-breadcrumbs\"><a href=\"/\">Home</a><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><span>Dog Parks Directory</span><i class=\"bi bi-chevron-right\"></i><strong>Wilson</strong></div><p class=\"hero-eyebrow\">City of Innovation</p><h1>Wilson Whirls</h1><div class=\"hero-chip-row\"><div class=\"hero-chip\"><span class=\"chip-label\">Dog Park</span><span class=\"chip-value\">yes</span></div><div class=\"hero-chip\"><span class=\"chip-label\">Art Park</span><span class=\"chip-value\">Unique</span></div></div><p class=\"hero-description\">Wilson is famous for its Whirligig Park, but its investment in pet amenities is just as impressive. The Wilson Dog Park and Lake Wilson offer diverse experiences.</p><div class=\"city-rich-description\"><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">Wilson, North Carolina, offers a dog-friendly experience that is infused with art and innovation. The <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.wilsonwhirligigpark.org\">Vollis Simpson Whirligig Park</a> provides a stunning backdrop for a walk, with massive, kinetic sculptures spinning overhead. Leashed dogs are welcome in this green space, making for a walk unlike any other in the state. It serves as the anchor for a revitalized downtown that is becoming increasingly walkable and welcoming.</p><p class=\"rich-description-paragraph\">For specialized canine recreation, the <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.wilsonnc.org/government/departments/parks-recreation/dog-park\">Wilson Dog Park</a> on Lawndale Drive is excellent. It features agility equipment, water stations, and separate areas for different sized dogs, showing the city’s commitment to providing high-quality amenities. Additionally, the loop trail around Lake Wilson offers a serene escape for those looking to enjoy nature. Wilson proves that a city can support both cultural tourism and a practical, <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"rich-link\" href=\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\">pet-friendly lifestyle</a>.</p></div><div class=\"hero-cta-row\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta primary\"><i class=\"bi bi-list-check\"></i>Browse directory</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"hero-cta ghost\"><i class=\"bi bi-geo-alt\"></i>Open map</button><a class=\"hero-cta text-link\" href=\"/list-your-park\"><i class=\"bi bi-plus-circle\"></i>Submit a park</a></div><div class=\"hero-footnotes\"><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Wilson Dog Park</span><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Whirligig Park</span><span><i class=\"bi bi-sparkles\"></i> <!-- -->Lake Wilson</span></div></div><div class=\"city-hero-visual\"><div class=\"hero-image-card\"><img alt=\"Wilson dog park landscape\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\" src=\"/images/cities/wilson-nc/hero.png\"/><div class=\"hero-image-gradient\"></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"city-premium-section\" aria-labelledby=\"city-premium-heading\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"city-premium-header\"><div><span class=\"section-eyebrow\">Premium spotlight</span><h2 id=\"city-premium-heading\">Premium parks in <!-- -->Wilson</h2><p>Partners highlighted here are currently investing in featured placement across this guide.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-header-actions\"><a class=\"hero-cta primary\" href=\"/list-your-park\">Feature my park</a><a class=\"hero-cta ghost\" href=\"/contact\">Talk to sales</a></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-values\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-megaphone\"></i></div><h4>Pinned above free listings</h4><p>Premium partners appear before every other card within the city directory.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-envelope-paper\"></i></div><h4>Lead-friendly CTAs</h4><p>Direct website + phone buttons encourage bookings straight from this page.</p></div><div class=\"city-premium-value-card\"><div class=\"city-premium-value-icon\"><i class=\"bi bi-clock-history\"></i></div><h4>Always-on exposure</h4><p>Featured cards show even when we haven’t processed new static data yet.</p></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-grid\"><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div><div class=\"city-premium-card animate-pulse\"><div class=\"city-premium-media bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"h-4 w-1/2 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-2 h-3 w-3/4 rounded bg-slate-200\"></div><div class=\"mt-4 h-16 rounded bg-slate-100\"></div></div></div></div></section><section id=\"city-insights\" class=\"city-insights-section\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><section id=\"city-statistics\" class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db city-stats-unified\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-section-header\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-eyebrow\">City Statistics</span><h2 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">How <!-- -->Wilson<!-- --> stacks up for dog families</h2><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stats-intro\">Wilson is unique. You can walk your dog beneath massive kinetic sculptures in the morning and let them romp in a dedicated dog park in the afternoon.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stats-row\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card accent\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Top Spot</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Wilson Dog Park</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">A well-equipped facility with agility tunnels, water stations, and separate play areas. The social center for pets.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Art Walk</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Whirligig Park</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">A one-of-a-kind park featuring massive wind-powered sculptures. Leashed dogs are welcome on the lawns.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db quick-stat-card \"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-tag\">Nature</span><h3 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-value\">Lake Wilson</h3><p class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db stat-copy\">A beautiful 2-mile walking loop around the lake. Scenic, peaceful, and perfect for exercise.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db data-grid-container\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db key-metrics-grid\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item primary\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-geo-alt-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">14</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Total Dog Parks</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">All types combined</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-star-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">4.6</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Average Rating</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">Based on <!-- -->3,063<!-- --> reviews</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-chat-heart-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">3,063</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Total Reviews</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">Community feedback</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-icon\"><i class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bi bi-trophy-fill\"></i></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-details\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-number\">9</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-label\">Premium Parks</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db metric-sub\">4.5+ star ratings</span></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db charts-grid\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chart-card\"><h4 class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db\">Park Types Distribution</h4><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db chart-content\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bar-item\"><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bar-header\"><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bar-label\">Indoor Dog Park</span><span class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bar-value\">14<!-- --> parks</span></div><div class=\"jsx-9f62ad4bc1f1d4db bar-track\"><div style=\"w