ere is the Wilson Dog Park?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"The Wilson Dog Park is located at 1413 Lawndale Dr. It’s a fenced facility with separate areas for large and small dogs, plus agility tunnels.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Are dogs allowed at the Whirligig Park?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes! Leashed dogs are welcome in Vollis Simpson Whirligig Park. It’s a unique spot for a walk, but keep an eye on your dog around the moving sculptures.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Does Wilson have greenways?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, the Wilson Greenway System is growing. The beautifully paved path around Lake Wilson is a particularly scenic spot for a 2-mile dog walk.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What are the leash laws in Wilson?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Dogs must be on a leash and under physical control when off the owner’s property. Wilson takes animal control seriously to ensure public safety.\"}}]}4:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$d\"}}]\n5:[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"suppressHydrationWarning\":true,\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"BreadcrumbList\\\",\\\"itemListElement\\\":[{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":1,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Home\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":2,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Dog Parks Directory\\\",\\\"item\\\":\\\"https://www.indoordogpark.org/\\\"},{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ListItem\\\",\\\"position\\\":3,\\\"name\\\":\\\"Wilson\\\"}]}\"}}]\n6:[\"$\",\"$Le\",null,{\"variant\":\"light\"}]\n7:[\"$\",\"$Lf\",null,{\"items\":[{\"id\":\"city-hero\",\"title\":\"City Overview\",\"level\":1},{\"id\":\"city-insights\",\"title\":\"Quick Facts\",\